name: Hard To Beat Me
tagline: An original game using Etyllica Engine made in Dumativa at Global Game Jam 2013.
body:
### Hard To Beat Me
The game was developed in 48h hours during the Global Game Jam 2013. I used [http://yuripourre.github.com/etyllica](Etyllica Engine) originally with JavaSound to play music.

Later, I changed the old audio library to [http://www.paulscode.com/forum/index.php?topic=4.0](SoundSystem) with JoAL.
